::Shadow Wing::

She looked around. "No, I have nothing to move.  What little I had is now 
gone. Let's just go to.  It's getting depressing around here with the old 
base in ruin." She looked around at the old base one more time.
"Yeah, let's go."

The new base is in Africa.

::Prowl::

Prowl shakes his head. All the devices that they could possibly need were 
destroyed in the last attack.

"No, there's nothing to bring. Everything's kinda destroyed," he says, "But 
after you're done moving, you can help us fix this dump."
